HEADWORD: Similor
<hw>Sim"i*lor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>similus</ets> similar + F. <ets>or</ets> gold, L. <ets>aurum</ets>.
